<br>
I'd like to add something to my original post here.  Whilst I can understand why some people might be uncomfortable with looking at people kissing, and some people might be even more uncomfortable being confronted with homosexual men kissing, personally, I really don't mind Robin's signature at all.  <br>
<br>
Sure, it makes me feel a little uncomfortable (flashback parent thing and some other personal issues from my past which I won't bore you all with here) ... but it's good to be made to feel uncomfortable at times.   <br>
<br>
I completely respect Robin's right to express himself in any manner he wishes (within the bounds of public decency of course).   We see heterosexual couples embracing on our television screens on a regular basis, at any time of the day or night totally unrestricted by the watershed.  It is deemed acceptable for children and adults alike to view people kissing.... and rightly so.  There is nothing wrong with it.  It's a perfectly healthy part of a relationship. <br>
<br>
To say that it is acceptable to view heterosexual couples kissing but not homosexual couples kissing is wrong.  Yes, we may feel uncomfortable seeing it, but that is our problem and one we should keep to ourselves so hopefully our children will grow up to accept that this is okay and not something to be embarrassed about or ashamed of.  Because it is okay, and it's only the prejudices of our forefathers that have made it something that is wrong and sinful.  We have an obligation to our children to extinguish this prejudice and any others.  <br>
<br>
So, I applaud you Robin.... keep crusading, hon. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.geocities.com/pet0512/caliopae.txt"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=irexes>Irexes</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Live evil</span><br>  Posts: 603<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(3/9/03 10:46 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm49.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=35.topic&index=111>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: .... </span><hr size=1> Adriian, the bus for Tribunal left last week.<br>
